---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Help & Troubleshooting | LagSync">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 flex-grow">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-['Space_Mono'] uppercase tracking-tight">Help <span class="text-cyan-500">Center</span></h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-12">Common solutions for Bluetooth audio synchronization issues.</p>

      <div class="grid gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-[#111] border border-white/5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 font-['Space_Mono']">The sync works, but then drifts over time?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">This is common with long-form content. LagSync v1.0 will include logic that attempts to re-align the buffer every 1.5 seconds. If it drifts, try toggling the extension Off and On to reset the MSE hook.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-[#111] border border-white/5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 font-['Space_Mono']">Does it work with Disney+ or Amazon Prime?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Yes. As long as the site uses standard HTML5 Video or MediaSource Extensions (MSE), LagSync can intercept the audio stream.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-[#111] border border-white/5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 font-['Space_Mono']">I see "No video detected" in the popup.</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Ensure the video has actually started playing. Some players hide the <code class="text-cyan-400">&lt;video&gt;</code> element until the first frame is loaded. Refreshing the page usually solves this.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-cyan-500/5 border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-2xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Still need help?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6">Our developers respond to technical inquiries within 24 hours.</p>
        <a href="mailto:support@lagsync.com" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>